summary: Completed comprehensive testing of OMNISupply.io enhanced features including Infosys BPM branding, UNSPSC codes, cart functionality, and Order History tabs. All major features working correctly.

minor_bugs.impact: Chat history feature not working, but main chat functionality works

design_issues.issue: Some external logo images fail to load (ERR_NAME_NOT_RESOLVED)

passed_tests: Landing page displays Infosys BPM logo in navbar
Bento grid shows Products (30M+) and Services (100K+) cards side by side
Login page shows Infosys BPM logo
Sidebar shows Infosys BPM logo after login
Product cards display UNSPSC codes (format: UNSPSC: 31170000)
Service cards display UNSPSC codes (format: UNSPSC: 76111501)
Cart button in header works and opens cart drawer
Add to Cart button adds products to cart
PunchOut transfer modal shows all 5 systems: Coupa, SAP Ariba, SAP ERP, Ivalua, Oracle
Order History page has 4 tabs: Orders, PunchOut Transfers, Quotations, RFQs
All Order History tabs are clickable and functional
Backend API endpoints working (16/17 tests passed - 94.1% success rate)
Login functionality with demo@infosys.com / demo123 / USA
UNSPSC codes properly displayed on both products and services
